{"tid":761500,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"垃圾缺德冇品香港人","createTime":"2018-07-30T12:18:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-01T06:43:16.000Z","uid":192780,"like":18,"dislike":41,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"10817c040c305d9ea55a9344f3e107b52b0691f6","tid":761500,"uid":192780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T12:18:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/30/194914_0055a190cdf44b6030eda9b66c43f1e9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F30%2F194914_0055a190cdf44b6030eda9b66c43f1e9.png&h=af9ea0ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n剩係排隊就已經睇到你地香港人係幾咁冇公德<br />\n頭先放工等小巴走<br />\n去到小巴站已經有四個人係到排緊隊<br />\n我真係唔撚明點解你班垃圾香港人可以連隊都唔識排<br />\n好地地順住小巴站條行人路排隊唔得既<br />\n係要攔腰劏開人地幾條線黎排隊(見圖)<br />\n結果我冇跟住隊尾排<br />\n我照企行人路等<br />\n但條氣真係谷住谷住<br />\n忍唔住望住條人龍講<br />\n「如果條龍好長 你地咁排咪霸晒條路」<br />\n我講完啲人都不為所動<br />\n<br />\n我真係見過啲人咁樣排隊好多次<br />\n點解你地香港人明明見到有人錯左都會照跟<br />\n<br />\n如果你係我<br />\n你會好似我咁排嘗試撥亂反正就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n定<br />\n照排隊尾就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be29acb03784e0d6ef7e620c2487f65b9e5744b3","tid":761500,"uid":176366,"like":24,"dislike":3,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T12:34:32.000Z","msg":"剩係排隊就已經睇到<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>你地</strong></span>香港人係幾咁冇公德<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c354936394ec0a52f9a4e01f35333cfec53ff94","tid":761500,"uid":192780,"like":7,"dislike":22,"score":-15,"quote":{"pid":"be29acb03784e0d6ef7e620c2487f65b9e5744b3","tid":761500,"uid":176366,"like":24,"dislike":3,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T12:34:32.000Z","msg":"剩係排隊就已經睇到<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>你地</strong></span>香港人係幾咁冇公德<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"20